555
00:38:23,500 --> 00:38:27,060
[Yan City]

556
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:56,940
Master!

557
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,380
Senior Brother.

558
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:05,490
Tingyan.

559
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:25,090
