570
00:39:52,030 --> 00:39:53,780
Oh, my girl has truly grown up.

571
00:39:56,440 --> 00:39:59,780
That Black Serpent probably won't stay put either.

572
00:40:02,320 --> 00:40:03,050
What do you mean?

573
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:08,970
