574
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:11,940
Now Hei Nianjiu can't stop fawning over her.

575
00:40:12,150 --> 00:40:14,450
Mu Nisheng has strategy and vision.

576
00:40:15,030 --> 00:40:16,420
She's perfect for a general.

577
00:40:18,150 --> 00:40:20,450
You are clever and quick-witted.

578
00:40:21,320 --> 00:40:22,780
