584
00:40:38,150 --> 00:40:39,420
All right...

585
00:40:53,070 --> 00:40:54,010
I'm here for Hongluo.

586
00:41:00,190 --> 00:41:00,900
Nianjiu,

587
00:41:01,550 --> 00:41:04,220
