588
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:06,170
that feelings took time to grow.

589
00:41:06,760 --> 00:41:08,380
But I left something out.

590
00:41:13,550 --> 00:41:16,170
Once those feelings are deep enough,

591
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:19,340
you must seize the moment,

592
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:20,940
or you'll lose your chance.

593
00:41:24,510 --> 00:41:25,090
Good luck.

594
00:41:38,400 --> 00:41:39,170
Hongluo.

595
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,260
What is it?

596
00:41:46,510 --> 00:41:47,970
This is Qiling nectar

597
00:41:49,030 --> 00:41:50,420
I brought back from Serene Vale.

598
00:41:51,550 --> 00:41:54,490
They say it strengthens the lungs

599
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:55,860
and nourishes the Seven Senses.

600
00:41:57,630 --> 00:41:58,300
Maybe

601
00:41:59,070 --> 00:42:00,490
it will help you

602
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:02,700
remember some of your past.

603
00:42:05,030 --> 00:42:06,490
I don't like sweets.

604
00:42:07,760 --> 00:42:08,380
Hongluo,

605
00:42:09,280 --> 00:42:10,820
I know you want to turn it down again,

606
00:42:12,320 --> 00:42:14,260
