610
00:42:25,840 --> 00:42:29,260
Since then, I've always been drawn to you.

611
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:33,450
But I was newly human then.

612
00:42:34,150 --> 00:42:35,220
I didn't realize

613
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:38,220
you were someone who kept

614
00:42:38,240 --> 00:42:39,610
everything hidden deep inside.

615
00:42:40,110 --> 00:42:41,010
I'm sorry.

616
00:42:42,470 --> 00:42:45,300
I let you bear

617
00:42:46,070 --> 00:42:47,420
